cts including pistons piston rings piston pins cylinder liners valve seats and guides engine valves and bearings industrial bearings bushings and washers ignition products dynamic seals bonded piston seals combustion and exhaust gaskets static gaskets and seals rigid heat shields flexible heat shields element resistant sleeving products and lighting products the motorparts segment provides light and commercial vehicle dis federalmogul holdings llc supplies various components accessories and systems to the manufacturers and servicers of vehicles and equipment worldwide it operates through two segments powertrain and motorparts the powertrain segment offers various products including pistons piston rings piston pins cylinder liners valve seats and guides engine valves and bearings industrial bearings bushings and washers ignition products dynamic seals bonded piston seals combustion and exhaust gaskets static gaskets and seals rigid heat shields flexible heat shields element resistant sleeving products and lighting products the motorparts segment provides light and commercial vehicle disc pads light vehicle drum brake linings commercial vehicle full length linings commercial vehicle half blocks railway brake blocks driveline universal joints combustion and exhaust gaskets static gaskets and seals wipers filters pistons piston rings cylinder liners and ignition and lighting products as well as chassis parts such as ball joints tie rod ends sway bar links idler arms pitman arms and control arms federalmogul holdings llc offers its products under the wagner abex ferodo jurid stop quickstop thermoquiet oex beral moog quicksteer felpro payen goetze national anco champion interfil sealed power speed pro fp diesel nüral and beru names the company serves original equipment manufacturers and servicers of automotive light and medium and heavyduty commercial vehicles and offroad agricultural marine rail aerospace power generation and industrial equipment markets as well as various distributors retail parts stores and mass merchants federalmogul holdings llc was founded in  and is headquartered in southfield michigan federalmogul holdings llc is a subsidiary of ieh fm holdings llc detailed description  west  mile roadsouthfield mi united statesfounded in  employees phone  wwwfederalmogulcom key executives for federalmogul holdings llc mr rainer jueckstock cochairman cochief executive officer and chief executive officer of powertrain age  mr bradley s norton cochairman of the board coceo and ceo of federalmogul motorparts age  mr jerome rouquet chief financial officer and senior vice president age  mr martin m hendricks president of global braking global wipers and emea federalmogul motorparts age  mr andrew d sexton president of emea for federalmogul motorparts age  compensation as of fiscal year  federalmogul holdings llc key developments federalmogul holdings llc files form  feb   federalmogul holdings llc has announced that it has filed a form  with the securities and exchange commission to voluntarily deregister its common stock under the securities exchange act of  as amended the par value of the companys common stock was  per share federalmogul holdings llc reports unaudited consolidated earnings results for the fourth quarter and full year ended december   feb   federalmogul holdings llc reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the fourth quarter and full year ended december   for the quarter the company reported net sales of  million compared to  million a year ago operating income was  million compared to operating loss of  million a year ago income from continuing operations before income taxes was  million compared to loss from continuing operations before income taxes of  million a year ago net income attributable to the company was  million or  per basic and diluted share compared to net loss attributable to the company of  million or  per basic and diluted share a year ago ebitda was  million compared to  million a