 board of directors federalmogul motorparts sells and distributes a broad portfolio of products through more than  of the world’s most recognized brands in the global vehicle aftermarket while also serving original equipment vehicle manufacturers with products including braking chassis wipers and other vehicle components  the company’s aftermarket brands include anco® wiper blades champion® spark plugs wipers and filters ae® felpro® fp diesel® goetze® glyco® nüral® payen® and sealed power® engine products moog® chassis components and ferodo® jurid® and wagner® brake products federalmogul powertrain designs and manufactures original equipment powertrain components and systems protection products for automotive heavyduty industrial and transport applications federalmogul was founded in detroit in  and maintains its worldwide headquarters in southfield michigan the company employs nearly  in  countries     request more information tweet share federalmogul holdings corp load more content federalmogul holdings corp federalmogul abex rx  lining in brake system home drivetrains brake system federalmogul abex rx  brake lining federalmogul abex rx  brake lining the federalmogul abex rx  brake lining helps is capable of delivering a stopping distance of  ft from  mph when used on a loaded truck with a  lb drive axle federalmogul holdings corp may   federalmogul motorparts a division of federalmogul holdings corp has expanded its range of abex reduced stopping distance rsd certified commercial grade friction linings to include the abex rx  lining provides excellent lining and drum wear exceeds both the federal motor vehicle safety standards fmvss  reduced stopping distance rsd requirement and oe brake manufacturer standard for lb  kg tractor applications capable of delivering stopping distance of just  ft  m from  mph  kmh on a tractor equipped with a pound drive axle and pound steer axle under loaded conditions beating fmvss  rsd standard and oe brake manufacturer requirement