ty federalmogul’s powertrain global purchasing is responsible for procuring all goods and services used by federalmogul powertrain and our joint ventures around the world sourcing decisions are made based on suppliers’ performance in quality service and cost the goal of global purchasing is to improve communications with our supply base in order to generate efficiencies and enhance product quality in order to make the most productive use of our website current federalmogul powertrain suppliers should review our powertrain purchasing and diversity policies download relevant documents log in to your supplynet account at least once a month prospective suppliers should review our powertrain purchasing and diversity policies initiate the supplier registration process announcements supplier code of conduct letter module contents explore federalmogul powertrain careers                                                               explore federalmogul motorparts careers  federalmogul llc  site map  privacy policy  legal disclaimer  social media  modern slavery policy fmcorporatepubmaster pages federalmogul corporation english english chinese financials media suppliers company faq contact us      oe pistons • sealing • systems protection • bearings • ignition rings  liners • valve seats and guides • valvetra​in      oe braking • chassis • wipers aftermarket components module contents          explore federalmogul powertrain careers                                                               explore federalmogul motorparts careers  federalmogul llc  site map  privacy policy  legal disclaimer  social media  modern slavery policy fmcorporatepubmaster pages safety data sheets msds english english chinese financials media suppliers company faq contact us home  company  safety data sheets company overview corporate leaders board of directors corporate governance code of conduct audit committee charter code of ethics corporate governance culture and diversity corporate social res